title: Engineered wood plank flooring throughout
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Brushed stainless kitchen faucet with pull-down sprayer', '-High Intensity UVC Lamp Coupled with Bionic iWave Air Purifying Systems', '-Certified 100% sprinklered apartments', '-Engineered wood plank flooring throughout', '-Heated, Underground Garage Stalls Available with Convenient Car Washing Station', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-The Cinema Offers Cozy Seating for Private Viewing Parties', '-The Event Features a Demonstration Kitchen with Enough Room to Entertain a Few Close Friends or a Crowd', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Large, Glass-Enclosed Indoor Pool, Sauna and Steam Room Open Year Round', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
